item.title: 【Live Audios (lossless)】FLAC - Björk - Live at Manchester Academy, 09-14-1993 [FM Broadcast FLAC]
item.description:
​
A newly de-Sugarcubed Björk on her first solo tour, an FM broadcast from the Manchester Academy. It's a bouncy set of her off-beat art pop, including almost every song from Debut (only 'Aeroplane' is missing), augmented by a B-side and one of the earliest performances of 'Army of Me'.

Track listing:
  1. Human Behaviour
  2. Atlantic
  3. One Day
  4. Venus as a Boy
  5. Come to Me
  6. The Anchor Song
  7. Play Dead
  8. Crying
  9. Violently Happy
  10. There's More to Life Than This
  11. Big Time Sensuality
  12. Army of Me
